    "description": "The jNet Citadel-OS on Atmel AT90SC144144CT is a Personal Identity Verification Smart Card, HSPD-12 implementation with dual interface I/O. The secure, smart card native OS is fully compliant with NIST 800-73-1 and FIPS PUB 201-1 requirements. The module is used for physical and logical access control to government resources. The AT90SC144144CT is a low-power, high-performance, 8/16-bit microcontroller with Flash program memory and EEPROM data memory, based on the secureAVR enhanced RISC architecture.",
